About this item

  • Sophisticated Glass Workspace: Elevate your office with ErGear's tempered glass standing desk featuring an elegant tabletop that combines style and functionality, perfect for dry-erase notes or artwork.
  • Durable and Stable Design: Equipped with dual motors rigorously tested for 50,000 cycles, this adjustable desk ensures long-lasting durability and stability, even under heavy loads.
  • Integrated Convenience: The smart control panel with USB and Type-C ports offers convenient charging for your devices, while the partitioned drawer provides organized storage for office essentials.
  • Ergonomic Height Adjustments: Quickly transition between your preferred ergonomic positions with four programmable memory buttons, adjusting the desk height from 27.9" to 46.4" at 0.98" per second for maximum comfort and productivity.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

About this Item

  • Sophisticated Glass Workspace: Elevate your office with ErGear's tempered glass standing desk featuring an elegant tabletop that combines style and functionality, perfect for dry-erase notes or artwork.
  • Durable and Stable Design: Equipped with dual motors rigorously tested for 50,000 cycles, this adjustable desk ensures long-lasting durability and stability, even under heavy loads.
  • Integrated Convenience: The smart control panel with USB and Type-C ports offers convenient charging for your devices, while the partitioned drawer provides organized storage for office essentials.
  • Ergonomic Height Adjustments: Quickly transition between your preferred ergonomic positions with four programmable memory buttons, adjusting the desk height from 27.9" to 46.4" at 0.98" per second for maximum comfort and productivity.
